title: Conference #3
description:
Title: How to reach your first 100K downloads organically
Speaker: Randy Saborío | Android Stateside’s Tech Lead
Description: Memorigi is a different, beautiful todo list, task planner, and reminder app made 100% in Costa Rica. It’s located within the top 10 apps (#8) for ‘todo’ search term in Google Play Store next to enterprise apps like Wunderlist (#5), Any.do (#6), and TickTickTick (#7), beating Trello (#11), GTasks (#12), and Evernote (#13).
In this keynote you’ll learn how to reach thousands of downloads for your app and how to keep your user base growing consistently and organically.
